    <info xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:lang="en">
        <title>The SSML Integration Feature </title>
        <annotation annotates="/">
            <para>The Z39.98 SSML Integration Feature recasts a subset of the W3C Speech Synthesis Markup Language (SSML) Version 1.1 as a Feature for incorporation in Z39.98-2012 Profiles. </para>
        </annotation>
